ost\u011bjov, [[Olomouc Region]]}}\n| Male\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | Husband of an infected woman (Case # 46). Both were skiing in Italy.<ref name=\"case45-46\">{{cite web|url=https://olomoucky.denik.cz/zpravy_region/olomoucky-kraj-koronavirus-nakazeni-2020.html|title=The Olomouc Region already has 3 infected with coronavirus|website=olomoucky.denik.cz|access-date=2020-03-10}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''46'''\n| 10 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Italy}}\n| [[Litovel]]\n| [[Olomouc Region]]\n| {{Partial failure|Hospital in Prost\u011bjov, [[Olomouc Region]]}}\n| Female\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | Wife of an infected man (Case # 45). Both were skiing in Italy.<ref name=\"case45-46\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''47-63'''\n| 10 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{n/a}}\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{n/a}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | No details yet.<ref name=\"case43-61\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''64'''\n| 11 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Italy}}, [[Livigno]]\n| {{n/a}}\n| [[Pilsen Region]]\n| {{n/a}}\n| Female\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | A woman returning from Livigno.<ref name=\"case64\">{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/adamvojtechano/status/1237637984058515463|title=Minister of Health announces case 64|website=Twitter/AdamVojtechAno|access-date=2020-03-10}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''65'''\n| 11 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Italy}}, [[Trentino]]\n| {{n/a}}\n| [[Zlin Region]]\n| {{n/a}}\n| Male\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{n/a}}\n|- class=\"expa