o|title=\u0158idi\u010d Uberu byl podle hygieny v kontaktu s t\u00e9m\u011b\u0159 stovkou lid\u00ed. Nakazit ho mohli n\u011bme\u010dt\u00ed klienti Airbnb|website=iROZHLAS}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''39'''\n| 10 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{Partial failure|Person-to-person spread}}\n| {{flagicon|CZE}} workplace\n| {{n/a}}\n| [[Central Bohemian Region]]\n| {{n/a}}\n| Female\n| ~61\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | A woman (*1959) from Central Bohemia contracted the virus at work where she had been in contact with a woman infected at Val Gardena ski resort in Italy.<ref name=case39.twitter>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/adamvojtechano/status/1237257274541965312|title=Minister of Health announces case 39|website=Twitter/AdamVojtech|access-date=2020-03-10}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''40'''\n| 10 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Italy}}, [[Sexten]]\n| {{n/a}}\n| [[\u00dast\u00ed nad Labem Region]]\n| {{n/a}}\n| Male\n| ~54\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | A man (*1966) has returned from skiing in Sexten, Italy.<ref name=case40.twitter>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/adamvojtechano/status/1237257388157210624|title=Minister of Health announces case 40|website=Twitter/AdamVojtech|access-date=2020-03-10}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''41'''\n| 10 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Germany}}\n| [[Prost\u011bjov]]\n| [[Olomouc Region]]\n| {{Partial failure|Hospital in Prost\u011bjov, [[Olomouc Region]]}}\n| Male\n| ~55\n| {{flag|JPN}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | An employee of Japanese origin of company Toray Textiles Central Europe in Prost\u011bjov. The patient returned from Germany with high fever. After spending initial week in home isolati