il na hasi\u010dsk\u00e9 z\u00e1bav\u011b - Novinky.cz|website=www.novinky.cz}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=6 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''Social distancing measures'''\n| '''Public authorities' activity reduction'''\n| 12 March 2020\n| 14 March to 1 April.\n\nExtended until 11 April.\n| Public authorities restricted to perform only to necessary duties. Restrictions on duties requiring personal contact with the public. Restriction of office hours to 3 hours on Monday and Wednesday. Only the lowest possible number of employees to be present when necessary. Duty to implement rotations of employees in a way that prevents contact between selected groups.\n\n'''Partially revoked on 6 April 2020''': {{Interlanguage link|Czechpoint|cs|Czech POINT}} resumes service.\n| Government Resolution No. 194/2000 (until 24 March)\n\nMinistry of Health Protection Measure No. MZDR 12745/2020-3/MIN/KAN (from 24 March onwards)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mzcr.cz/Soubor.ashx?souborID=40684&typ=application/pdf&nazev=Mimo%C5%99%C3%A1dn%C3%A9%20opat%C5%99en%C3%AD%20-%20prodlou%C5%BEen%C3%AD%20omezen%C3%AD%20%C4%8Dinnosti%20OVM%20a%20SO.pdf |title=Info |publisher=www.mzcr.cz |date= |accessdate=2020-04-06}}</ref>\n\nMinistry of Health Protection Measure No. MZDR 12745/2020-5/MIN/KAN (from 1 April onwards)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mzcr.cz/Soubor.ashx?souborID=40760&typ=application/pdf&nazev=Mimo%C5%99%C3%A1dn%C3%A9%20opat%C5%99en%C3%AD%20-%20prodlou%C5%BEen%C3%AD%20na%C5%99%C3%ADzen%C3%AD%20omezen%C3%A9ho%20provozu%20OVM%20a%20SO.pdf |title=Info |publisher=www.mzcr.cz |date= |accessdate=2020-04-06}}</ref>\n\nMinistry of Health Protection Measure No. MZDR 15190/2020-2/MIN/KAN (Czechpoint reopening)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mzcr.cz/Soubor.ashx?souborID=40880&typ=application/pdf&nazev=Ukon%C4%8Den%C3%AD%20mimo%C5%99%C3%A1dn%C3%A9ho%20opat%C5%99en%C3%AD%20ze%20dne%2030.%203.%202020%20ke%20kontaktn%C3%ADm%20m%C3%ADst%C5%AFm%20ve%C5%99ejn%C3%A9%20spr%C3%A1vy%20Czech%20POINT